Imo State Government has denied the reports of the State Governor, Hope Uzodimma being down with a stroke and has been rushed to India. According to the Imo State Commissioner for Information and Strategy, Declan Mbadiwe Emelumba, Uzodinma is hale and healthy as he has been devoting his attention to all scheduled activities in Abuja. Emelumba said, “Uzodinma is not afflicted with any challenge that would have led to a stroke. -Advertisement- “I don’t really know what those concocting this rumour want to achieve.”The Minister urged the general public to ignore such news, describing the false audio recording as a satanic fabrication.